<br>
You don't think this is an appropriate rogue topic?  Well, IMO this is the single biggest change in EQ since the introduction of levels 50-60.  Forget the whole Spells = Weapons debate.  Now Focus Items = Weapons.  Caster abilities will now be able to mudflate along with melee abilities.  Caster power will be directly related to equipment for a change.  <br>
<br>
For rogues, you will notice casters doing more damage, casting more spells, casting spells faster, and getting less aggro.  On a more positive note, you will notice your buffers and healers casting more, and casting faster, and their buffs will last longer.<br>
<br>
I appreciate that this is less obviously a rogue-related topic than say &quot;New Uber-Dagger found in XXXX&quot;; but it's going to impact on rogues and every other class in EQ hugely.<br>
